high_descs: Turn around and head towards the wooden shelves.
Pick up the cup on the bottom shelf.
Turn around and head towards the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the cup in front of the plate, close the fridge for the cup to cool down, and then open the fridge to take out the cup.
Place the cup next to the other cup on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Cool down a cup from the shelf.

high_descs: Go to the shelf behind you.
Take the rightmost cup from the second shelf.
